Men of God play critical roles in lives of men whether we choose to admit or not, explains Senate chief whip, Orji Uzor Kalu, recently to Daily Independent after he concluded a visit to St. Anthony’s Parish Amaekpu, Ohafia. Apart from being a homecoming reception Rev Michael Kalu Ukpong, the auxiliary bishop of Umuahia Diocese, the visit marks one of the many visits the former Abia State governor has embarked on in recent times as part of his social rapprochement and consultations. Aside his visit to his Ohafia home, the senator paid a courtesy visit to the revered Christian leader and  preacher Reverend Uma Ukpai. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! The Abia-North Senator arrived the Ohafia hilltop residence of the popular evangelist at exactly 12:30pm and proceeded to the inner residence where he and the Cleric spent few minutes in a brief engagement before taking his leave. In similar development, General Overseer of Light of the World International Church, Prophet Joshua Arogun has urged the Chief Whip of the Senate , Senator Orji Uzor Kalu to recognize other men of God who were instrumental to his spiritual life. Jitters In Osun Over Oyetola’s Second Term Bid Nigeria As A Failed State? The cleric said the Founder and President of LoveWorld Incorporated , also known as  Christ Embassy, Pastor Chris  Oyakhilome was not the only man of God that revealed to Kalu what happened to him in December 2019, adding that Kalu would be inviting the wrath of God if he ignores others. Prophet Joshua made the statements on Christmas day in Lagos during  the church’s ministration service to mark the birth of Jesus. He accused Kalu of selective appreciation and warned him of the impending dangers of such actions. He recalled that aside himself (Prohet Joshua ) other men of God like Pastor Enoch Adeboye of Redeemed Christian Church of 